<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT38">
<l>akaippiṉ maṉicarai yāṟu camayam</l>
<l>pukaittāṉ porukaṭalṉīr vaṇṇa ṉukaikkumē</l>
<l>lettēvar vālāṭṭu mevvāṟu ceykaiyu</l>
<l>mappō toḻiyu maḻaippu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He whose hue is that of the water of the dashing sea</l>
<l>Entraps humans devoid of uplifting [in] the six religions.</l>
<l>If [He] stirs up, any god’s arrogant deeds, any type of deeds,</l>
<l>[and] summons [to gods in the sacrifices] will cease then [and there].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
